name: Heart Caught Hold
description:
www.daxnorman.com

Hand Drawn Animated GIF

 by Dax Norman.

Gave my heart a hug.

I felt it inflate.

And then I flew,
Floating up .

Like a helium balloon,
Flying in the sky
With baby angels behind.

Right before,
Alone in a large room,
I thought i was home in a dream.
In a cavernous hallway
I wanted to sing.

Fractured reflections,
Didn't quite make sense.

A former friend, I told to go away.
I needed a place, a private space.

Then another familiar face jumped up.
From 30 feet below
"Heart Caught Hold"
